          </p>
          <div style={{background:"#FFFFFF",border:"1px solid #F0DED0",borderRadius:"16px",padding:"40px 36px",maxWidth:"560px",margin:"0 auto",boxShadow:"0 4px 24px rgba(232, 84, 140, 0.12)"}}>
            <p style={{fontSize:"13px",letterSpacing:"2px",textTransform:"uppercase",color:"#D63580",margin:"0 0 16px"}}>
