            What we're solving
          </p>
          <blockquote style={{borderLeft:"4px solid #FFD93D",paddingLeft:"28px",margin:"0 0 36px"}}>
            <p style={{fontSize:"clamp(19px, 3vw, 24px)",color:"#2D2D2D",margin:"0",lineHeight:"1.5",fontStyle:"italic"}}>
