            </p>
          </blockquote>
          <p style={{fontSize:"17px",color:"#5A4A42",margin:"0 0 22px",lineHeight:"1.75"}}>
            But the infrastructure around that work? The documentation, the protection, the structure that would let it move in the world without losing what makes it alive? That part hasn't been built yet.
          </p>
          <p style={{fontSize:"17px",color:"#5A4A42",margin:"0 0 40px",lineHeight:"1.75"}}>
