              <h3 style={{fontFamily:"Georgia, serif",fontSize:"16px",fontWeight:"bold",color:"#E8548C",margin:"0 0 10px"}}>
                Unnamed
              </h3>
              <p style={{fontSize:"14px",color:"#5A4A42",margin:"0",lineHeight:"1.65"}}>
                The frameworks and methodologies you use every day but have never formally documented.
